    "The amendment simplifies transaction cost calculations by using XRP directly, removing the complexity and potential for error in translating between 'fee units' and XRP.",
    "It standardizes the protocol by updating all instances of fee units to drops of XRP, improving clarity and consistency in the ledger data and fee voting protocol.",
